01:06:54.469 --> 01:06:56.554
- I still feel like
everyone's giving up.

1013
01:06:57.931 --> 01:07:00.141
Isn't there anything
else you guys can do?

1014
01:07:00.141 --> 01:07:03.603
- No. there is nothing more
that we can medically do

