01:08:11.629 --> 01:08:14.132
- So you're just
gonna kill him?!

1039
01:08:14.132 --> 01:08:14.966
- No. no.

1040
01:08:16.634 --> 01:08:18.970
Tiffany. unfortunately.
it is the cancer

1041
01:08:18.970 --> 01:08:20.346
